				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Thank you Marthisdil, for pointing out the obvious. Why even come out here and ask a question anymore? I said hey here's what I've been seeing I just showed one example of it and said had anyone else? I could go over my last weeks expierence in my post but since you seem so caught up in me stating definitives when all I did was ask a question based on my expierence I'll be obliged to go over all my expierence in the last week and a half. I never once stated anything or tryed to prove anything so I don't have to prove "Empirical proof" all I want are people's expierences. I don't have any time machines either so I couldn't jump back and go crunch numbers back then and compare them to now which "Empirical proof" would require.
<br />

<br />
I've done 14 ldon's in 4 days over those 4 day's I've noticed a definite jump in the amount of expierence I get while participating in these said dungeons.
<br />

<br />
I've been in over 8 raids over the last week, inlcuding Vex thal where I have also again noticed a big increase in the amount of expereince garnered while having leadership.
<br />

<br />
One of those raids also included some tactics killing, where I also noticed a bigger improvment in the amount of expierence I had racked up in a short amount of time. 
<br />

<br />
At tables in Fire I used to get half an orange every kite now I get about 3/4ths of an orange.
<br />

<br />
I'm not going to calculate, tri-angulate or coagulate anything or run tabs on things I'm not here to prove anyone right or wrong, all I want is a simple question answered without people jumping on me and saying rude things. I'm not stating it has been increased or it has been decreased all I'm saying is that I've noticed it going faster and if anyone else has. Period. Nothing more nothing less.</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Azmeka Raidner on Thu Mar 25, 2004 11:17 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
