I understand that.  Someone else though made a valid post about as you can't select the amount of xp that goes into leadership, just turn it on or off that if you have it on, by the time you get most of the useful leadership AA's, when will have earned every possible useful AA and many that are possibly useful.  IE, if you want leadership AA, turn it on whenever possible so you get those leadership AA's before you start getting "Improved wisdom."
<br />

